<div class="shop-container">
    <section class="shop-hero">
        <span class="eyebrow">FRESH DISPLAY</span>
        <h1>오늘 먹고 싶은 고기를 한눈에.</h1>
        <p>소, 돼지, 닭을 상황과 요리 목적별로 묶어 고객이 바로 고를 수 있게 구성했습니다.</p>
    </section>

    <div class="shop-scroll-layout">
        <%- include('../../partials/brand-spirit-card', { className: 'market-belief brand-spirit-card' }) %>

        <main class="shop-main-sections">
            <section class="shop-section product-scroll-section" id="boss-picks" data-visual="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1607623814075-e51df1bdc82f?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=85" data-title="사장추천 / 특가 상품">
                <div class="section-header">
                    <span class="badge secondary">BEST SELLER</span>
                    <h2>사장추천 / 특가 상품</h2>
                    <p>입고 상태와 판매 반응이 좋은 상품만 앞에 배치했습니다.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="product-grid">
                    <% if (sections.bossPicks.length > 0) { %>
                        <% sections.bossPicks.forEach(product => { %>
                            <%- include('card', { product }) %>
                        <% }) %>
                    <% } else { %>
                        <div class="empty-state">추천 메뉴를 준비 중입니다.</div>
                    <% } %>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="shop-section bg-alt product-scroll-section" id="theme-shop" data-visual="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1558030006-450675393462?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=85" data-title="어떤 메뉴로 해야지?">
                <div class="section-header">
                    <span class="badge accent">THEME SHOP</span>
                    <h2>어떤 메뉴로 해야지?</h2>
                    <p>홈파티, 집밥, 야식, 캠핑처럼 구매 상황에 맞춰 보여줍니다.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="theme-tabs">
                    <button class="theme-tab" data-theme="party">홈파티</button>
                    <button class="theme-tab" data-theme="home_meal">집밥</button>
                    <button class="theme-tab" data-theme="late_night">야식</button>
                    <button class="theme-tab" data-theme="camping">캠핑</button>
                </div>
                <div class="product-grid">
                    <% sections.homeParty.forEach(product => { %>
                        <%- include('card', { product }) %>
                    <% }) %>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="shop-section product-scroll-section" id="cooking-use-shop" data-visual="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1551028150-64b9f398f678?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=85" data-title="요리 용도용">
                <div class="section-header">
                    <span class="badge primary">COOKING CUT</span>
                    <h2>요리 용도용</h2>
                    <p>구이, 국·찌개, 볶음·불고기처럼 조리 방식에 맞는 판매 목록입니다.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="cooking-tabs">
                    <button class="cooking-tab" data-cooking="grill">구이용</button>
                    <button class="cooking-tab" data-cooking="soup_stew">국·찌개용</button>
                    <button class="cooking-tab" data-cooking="stir_fry_bulgogi">볶음·불고기용</button>
                    <button class="cooking-tab" data-cooking="braise">찜·조림용</button>
                    <button class="cooking-tab" data-cooking="boil_bossam_jangjorim">수육·보쌈·장조림용</button>
                </div>
                <div class="product-grid">
                    <% sections.cookingUse.forEach(product => { %>
                        <%- include('card', { product }) %>
                    <% }) %>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="shop-section product-scroll-section" id="family-shop" data-visual="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1604503468506-a8da13d82791?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=85" data-title="가족 식탁 추천">
                <div class="section-header">
                    <span class="badge primary">CARE SHOP</span>
                    <h2>가족 식탁 추천</h2>
                    <p>아이, 부모님, 1인 가구, 운동 식단까지 목적이 분명한 상품입니다.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="family-tabs">
                    <button class="family-tab" data-family="happy_table">가족행복 식탁</button>
                    <button class="family-tab" data-family="kids_safe">아이 안심 반찬</button>
                    <button class="family-tab" data-family="parents_care">부모님 보양</button>
                    <button class="family-tab" data-family="wellness_diet">웰빙/다이어트</button>
                    <button class="family-tab" data-family="mixed">혼합용</button>
                </div>
                <div class="product-grid family-product-grid">
                    <% sections.family.forEach(product => { %>
                        <div class="family-product" data-family="<%= product.family_category || 'mixed' %>">
                            <%- include('card', { product }) %>
                        </div>
                    <% }) %>
                </div>
            </section>
        </main>

        <aside class="visual-scroll-nav" aria-label="상품 사진 네비게이션">
            <div class="type-symbol-filter" aria-label="고기 종류 필터">
                <button type="button" data-type="all" title="전체"><span class="type-symbol all" aria-hidden="true">ALL</span></button>
                <button type="button" data-type="beef" title="소고기">
                    <span class="type-symbol animal animal-cow" aria-hidden="true">
                        <svg class="hanwoo-head" viewBox="0 0 64 64" focusable="false">
                            <path class="hanwoo-ear" d="M18 24 4 17l3 19 14-5M42 25l17-5-7 16-12-5"/>
                            <path class="hanwoo-horn" d="M24 18C18 9 17 4 21 2c7 3 9 10 9 17M42 18C49 9 50 4 46 2c-7 3-9 10-9 17"/>
                            <path class="hanwoo-face" d="M18 18c7-7 25-7 32 3 5 7 2 24-8 29-9 5-25 0-29-10-3-8-1-16 5-22Z"/>
                            <path class="hanwoo-muzzle" d="M12 39c7-5 20-3 24 4 1 7-6 13-17 10-8-2-11-9-7-14Z"/>
                            <path class="hanwoo-smile" d="M18 45c6 3 12 2 17-1"/>
                            <path class="hanwoo-cheek" d="M46 35c-2 5-5 8-9 10"/>
                            <circle class="hanwoo-eye" cx="39" cy="30" r="2.4"/>
                            <circle class="hanwoo-nose" cx="18" cy="44" r="1.6"/>
                        </svg>
                    </span>
                </button>
                <button type="button" data-type="pork" title="돼지고기"><span class="type-symbol animal animal-pig" aria-hidden="true">🐷</span></button>
                <button type="button" data-type="chicken" title="닭고기"><span class="type-symbol animal animal-chicken" aria-hidden="true">🐔</span></button>
                <button type="button" data-type="etc" title="세트"><span class="type-symbol set" aria-hidden="true">SET</span></button>
            </div>
            <div class="visual-card">
                <img id="floatingVisual" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1607623814075-e51df1bdc82f?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=85" alt="사장추천 / 특가 상품">
                <span id="floatingLabel">사장추천 / 특가 상품</span>
            </div>
            <div class="visual-dots">
                <a class="active" href="#boss-picks" data-target="boss-picks">사장추천 / 특가</a>
                <a href="#theme-shop" data-target="theme-shop">상황별 추천</a>
                <a href="#cooking-use-shop" data-target="cooking-use-shop">요리용도</a>
                <a href="#family-shop" data-target="family-shop">가족식탁</a>
            </div>
        </aside>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="cart-toast" role="status" aria-live="polite">장바구니에 담았습니다</div>

<script>
const visualSections = [...document.querySelectorAll('.product-scroll-section')];
const floatingVisual = document.getElementById('floatingVisual');
const floatingLabel = document.getElementById('floatingLabel');
const visualLinks = [...document.querySelectorAll('.visual-dots a')];
const productSections = [...document.querySelectorAll('.product-scroll-section')];
let activeSectionId = visualSections[0]?.id;
let visualTimer;
let visualPhotoIndex = 0;
let visualPhotoTimer;
let activeTypeFilter = null;
const prefersReducedMotion = window.matchMedia('(prefers-reduced-motion: reduce)').matches;

function sectionPhotos(section) {
    return [...section.querySelectorAll('.product-card:not(.carousel-clone) .card-image img')]
        .map(img => ({ src: img.currentSrc || img.src, alt: img.alt }))
        .filter(item => item.src);
}

function startVisualPhotoRotation(section) {
    clearInterval(visualPhotoTimer);
    const photos = sectionPhotos(section);
    if (!photos.length) return;
    visualPhotoIndex = 0;
    floatingVisual.src = photos[0].src;
    floatingVisual.alt = photos[0].alt || section.dataset.title;
    visualPhotoTimer = setInterval(() => {
        const latestPhotos = sectionPhotos(section);
        if (!latestPhotos.length) return;
        visualPhotoIndex = (visualPhotoIndex + 1) % latestPhotos.length;
        floatingVisual.classList.remove('is-sliding');
        void floatingVisual.offsetWidth;
        floatingVisual.src = latestPhotos[visualPhotoIndex].src;
        floatingVisual.alt = latestPhotos[visualPhotoIndex].alt || section.dataset.title;
        floatingVisual.classList.add('is-sliding');
    }, 1000);
}

function setActiveVisual(section) {
    if (!section || section.id === activeSectionId) return;
    activeSectionId = section.id;
    floatingLabel.textContent = section.dataset.title;
    startVisualPhotoRotation(section);
    visualLinks.forEach(link => link.classList.toggle('active', link.dataset.target === section.id));
}

function updateVisualOnScroll() {
    if (window.innerWidth < 1100) return;
    const viewportMiddle = window.innerHeight / 2;
    const closest = visualSections.reduce((best, section) => {
        const rect = section.getBoundingClientRect();
        const distance = Math.abs((rect.top + rect.height * 0.32) - viewportMiddle);
        return distance < best.distance ? { section, distance } : best;
    }, { section: visualSections[0], distance: Infinity }).section;
    setActiveVisual(closest);
}

window.addEventListener('scroll', updateVisualOnScroll, { passive: true });
window.addEventListener('resize', updateVisualOnScroll);
updateVisualOnScroll();
startVisualPhotoRotation(visualSections[0]);

function productElements(section) {
    return [...section.querySelectorAll('.product-card')]
        .filter(card => !card.closest('.carousel-clone'))
        .map(card => card.closest('.family-product') || card);
}

function visibleProductElements(section) {
    return productElements(section).filter(item => !item.hidden);
}

function animateVisibleCards(scope = document) {
    if (prefersReducedMotion) return;
    const cards = [...scope.querySelectorAll('.product-card:not(.carousel-clone)')]
        .filter(card => !card.hidden && !card.closest('[hidden]'));
    cards.forEach((card, index) => {
        card.classList.remove('is-card-visible');
        card.style.setProperty('--card-delay', `${Math.min(index, 7) * 55}ms`);
        window.setTimeout(() => card.classList.add('is-card-visible'), 20);
    });
}

function refreshCarousel(section) {
    const grid = section.querySelector('.product-grid');
    if (!grid) return;
    const visibleCount = visibleProductElements(section).length;
    grid.classList.toggle('is-carousel', visibleCount >= 4);
    if (visibleCount >= 4 && !grid.dataset.carouselReady) {
        setupCarousel(grid);
    }
    syncCarouselClones(section);
    animateVisibleCards(section);
}

function ensureCarouselClones(grid) {
    if (grid.dataset.clonesReady) return;
    [...grid.children].forEach(child => {
        const clone = child.cloneNode(true);
        clone.classList.add('carousel-clone');
        clone.setAttribute('aria-hidden', 'true');
        grid.appendChild(clone);
    });
    grid.dataset.clonesReady = 'true';
}

function syncCarouselClones(section) {
    const grid = section.querySelector('.product-grid');
    if (!grid) return;
    const originals = [...grid.children].filter(child => !child.classList.contains('carousel-clone'));
    const clones = [...grid.children].filter(child => child.classList.contains('carousel-clone'));
    clones.forEach((clone, index) => {
        const original = originals[index % originals.length];
        clone.hidden = !grid.classList.contains('is-carousel') || !original || original.hidden;
        clone.classList.toggle('is-fill-product', !!original?.classList.contains('is-fill-product'));
        clone.style.order = original ? String(Number(original.style.order || index) + 1000) : '';
    });
}

function showAllInSection(section) {
    section.querySelectorAll('.theme-tab, .cooking-tab, .family-tab').forEach(tab => tab.classList.remove('active'));
    productElements(section).forEach(item => {
        const card = item.classList.contains('product-card') ? item : item.querySelector('.product-card');
        item.classList.remove('is-fill-product');
        item.style.order = '';
        item.hidden = activeTypeFilter && card.dataset.category !== activeTypeFilter;
    });
    refreshCarousel(section);
}

function showAllProducts() {
    activeTypeFilter = null;
    document.querySelectorAll('.type-symbol-filter button').forEach(tab => tab.classList.remove('active'));
    productElements(document).forEach(item => {
        item.hidden = false;
        item.classList.remove('is-fill-product');
        item.style.order = '';
    });
    productSections.forEach(refreshCarousel);
    animateVisibleCards();
}

function filterProductsByCategory(category) {
    activeTypeFilter = category === 'all' ? null : category;
    document.querySelectorAll('.type-symbol-filter button').forEach(tab => {
        tab.classList.toggle('active', tab.dataset.type === category);
    });
    productElements(document).forEach(item => {
        const card = item.classList.contains('product-card') ? item : item.querySelector('.product-card');
        item.classList.remove('is-fill-product');
        item.style.order = '';
        item.hidden = category !== 'all' && card.dataset.category !== category;
    });
    productSections.forEach(refreshCarousel);
    animateVisibleCards();
}

document.querySelectorAll('.type-symbol-filter button').forEach(tab => {
    tab.addEventListener('click', () => {
        if (tab.dataset.type === 'all') {
            showAllProducts();
            tab.classList.add('active');
        } else {
            filterProductsByCategory(tab.dataset.type);
        }
    });
});

const themeTabs = [...document.querySelectorAll('.theme-tab')];
const themeSection = document.getElementById('theme-shop');
function applySectionSubFilter(section, key, value, activeTabs) {
    section.classList.add('is-filtering');
    activeTabs.forEach(tab => {
        const tabValue = tab.dataset.theme || tab.dataset.cooking || tab.dataset.family;
        tab.classList.toggle('active', tabValue === value);
    });

    const items = productElements(section).map((item, index) => {
        const card = item.classList.contains('product-card') ? item : item.querySelector('.product-card');
        const typeMatches = !activeTypeFilter || card.dataset.category === activeTypeFilter;
        const subMatches = card.dataset[key] === value || item.dataset[key] === value;
        item.hidden = true;
        item.classList.remove('is-fill-product');
        item.style.order = '';
        return { item, index, typeMatches, subMatches };
    });

    const selected = items.filter(entry => entry.typeMatches && entry.subMatches);
    const fillers = items.filter(entry => entry.typeMatches && !entry.subMatches).slice(0, Math.max(0, 4 - selected.length));

    selected.forEach((entry, index) => {
        entry.item.hidden = false;
        entry.item.style.order = String(index);
    });
    fillers.forEach((entry, index) => {
        entry.item.hidden = false;
        entry.item.classList.add('is-fill-product');
        entry.item.style.order = String(selected.length + index);
    });

    refreshCarousel(section);
    window.setTimeout(() => section.classList.remove('is-filtering'), 260);
}

themeTabs.forEach(tab => {
    tab.addEventListener('click', () => {
        applySectionSubFilter(themeSection, 'theme', tab.dataset.theme, themeTabs);
    });
});

const cookingTabs = [...document.querySelectorAll('.cooking-tab')];
const cookingSection = document.getElementById('cooking-use-shop');
cookingTabs.forEach(tab => {
    tab.addEventListener('click', () => {
        applySectionSubFilter(cookingSection, 'cooking', tab.dataset.cooking, cookingTabs);
    });
});

const familyTabs = [...document.querySelectorAll('.family-tab')];
function setFamilyCategory(category) {
    applySectionSubFilter(document.getElementById('family-shop'), 'family', category, familyTabs);
}
familyTabs.forEach(tab => {
    tab.addEventListener('click', () => setFamilyCategory(tab.dataset.family));
});

function setupCarousel(grid) {
    grid.dataset.carouselReady = 'true';
    ensureCarouselClones(grid);
    let paused = false;
    let dragging = false;
    let startX = 0;
    let startScrollLeft = 0;
    const speed = 0.32;

    const stop = () => { paused = true; };
    const resume = () => {
        if (!dragging) paused = false;
    };

    grid.addEventListener('mouseenter', stop);
    grid.addEventListener('mouseleave', resume);
    grid.addEventListener('touchstart', stop, { passive: true });
    grid.addEventListener('touchend', resume);
    grid.addEventListener('pointerdown', (event) => {
        dragging = true;
        paused = true;
        startX = event.clientX;
        startScrollLeft = grid.scrollLeft;
        grid.classList.add('is-dragging');
    });
    window.addEventListener('pointermove', (event) => {
        if (!dragging) return;
        grid.scrollLeft = startScrollLeft - (event.clientX - startX);
    });
    window.addEventListener('pointerup', () => {
        if (!dragging) return;
        dragging = false;
        grid.classList.remove('is-dragging');
        window.setTimeout(resume, 450);
    });

    function tick() {
        if (!paused && grid.classList.contains('is-carousel') && grid.scrollWidth > grid.clientWidth) {
            grid.scrollLeft += speed;
            if (grid.scrollLeft >= (grid.scrollWidth - grid.clientWidth) / 2) {
                grid.scrollLeft = 0;
            }
        }
        requestAnimationFrame(tick);
    }
    requestAnimationFrame(tick);
}

const sectionResetObserver = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
    entries.forEach(entry => {
        if (!entry.isIntersecting) return;
        showAllInSection(entry.target);
        if (entry.target.id === 'theme-shop') {
            themeTabs.forEach(tab => tab.classList.remove('active'));
        }
        if (entry.target.id === 'cooking-use-shop') {
            cookingTabs.forEach(tab => tab.classList.remove('active'));
        }
        if (entry.target.id === 'family-shop') {
            familyTabs.forEach(tab => tab.classList.remove('active'));
        }
    });
}, { threshold: 0.55 });

productSections.forEach(section => {
    sectionResetObserver.observe(section);
    refreshCarousel(section);
});

const cardRevealObserver = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
    entries.forEach(entry => {
        if (!entry.isIntersecting) return;
        entry.target.classList.add('is-card-visible');
        cardRevealObserver.unobserve(entry.target);
    });
}, { threshold: 0.18 });

document.querySelectorAll('.product-card:not(.carousel-clone)').forEach((card, index) => {
    card.style.setProperty('--card-delay', `${Math.min(index, 7) * 55}ms`);
    cardRevealObserver.observe(card);
});

document.addEventListener('click', (event) => {
    const button = event.target.closest('.cart-button');
    if (!button) return;

    button.classList.add('is-added');
    button.querySelector('.cart-label').textContent = '담김';
    const icon = button.querySelector('i');
    icon.className = 'fas fa-check';
    window.clearTimeout(button._cartTimer);
    const toast = document.querySelector('.cart-toast');
    if (toast) {
        toast.classList.remove('show');
        void toast.offsetWidth;
        toast.classList.add('show');
        window.clearTimeout(toast._timer);
        toast._timer = window.setTimeout(() => toast.classList.remove('show'), 1400);
    }
    button._cartTimer = window.setTimeout(() => {
        button.classList.remove('is-added');
        button.querySelector('.cart-label').textContent = '담기';
        icon.className = 'fas fa-plus';
    }, 1200);
});
</script>

<style>
.products-page-snap {
    scroll-snap-type: y mandatory;
    scroll-behavior: smooth;
}
.products-page-snap .shop-hero,
.products-page-snap .product-scroll-section {
    scroll-snap-align: start;
    scroll-margin-top: 96px;
}
.products-page-snap .product-scroll-section {
    min-height: calc(100vh - 82px);
}
.shop-container { padding-bottom: 50px; }
.shop-hero {
    padding: 56px 20px 34px;
    color: #fff;
    background:
        linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(33,79,53,0.88), rgba(143,23,29,0.58)),
        url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1529692236671-f1f6cf9683ba?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1500&q=85');
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center;
}
.shop-hero h1 {
    max-width: 1180px;
    margin: 8px auto;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 4rem);
    line-height: 1.05;
}
.shop-hero p,
.shop-hero .eyebrow {
    display: block;
    max-width: 1180px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
}
.shop-hero p {
    max-width: 560px;
    margin-top: 0;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.84);
    line-height: 1.7;
}
.shop-section {
    max-width: none;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 36px 0 24px;
}
.shop-scroll-layout {
    max-width: none;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 clamp(18px, 3vw, 48px);
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 220px minmax(760px, 1fr) 200px;
    gap: clamp(16px, 2vw, 28px);
    align-items: start;
}
.market-belief {
    position: sticky;
    top: 104px;
    min-height: calc(100vh - 190px);
}
.shop-main-sections {
    min-width: 0;
}
.shop-main-sections > .product-scroll-section > .product-grid {
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(min(100%, 200px), 240px));
    justify-content: start;
}
.product-grid.is-carousel {
    display: flex;
    overflow-x: auto;
    scroll-behavior: auto;
    scroll-snap-type: x proximity;
    cursor: grab;
    scrollbar-width: none;
    user-select: none;
}
.product-grid.is-carousel::-webkit-scrollbar {
    display: none;
}
.product-grid.is-carousel.is-dragging {
    cursor: grabbing;
    scroll-snap-type: none;
}
.product-grid.is-carousel > .product-card,
.product-grid.is-carousel > .family-product {
    flex: 0 0 calc((100% - 54px) / 4);
    min-width: 200px;
    scroll-snap-align: start;
}
.product-grid.is-carousel > .family-product[hidden],
.product-grid.is-carousel > .product-card[hidden] {
    display: none;
}
.product-grid:not(.is-carousel) > .carousel-clone {
    display: none;
}
.bg-alt {
    max-width: none;
    background: #fff6eb;
    padding-left: 18px;
    padding-right: 18px;
    padding-bottom: 24px;
    margin-top: 0;
    border-radius: 8px;
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
}
.section-header {
    margin-bottom: 16px;
}
.section-header h2 {
    margin: 10px 0 6px;
    font-size: clamp(1.55rem, 3vw, 2.25rem);
}
.section-header p {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
}
.theme-tabs,
.cooking-tabs {
    display: flex;
    gap: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    overflow-x: auto;
}
.family-tabs {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
}
.family-tab,
.cooking-tab {
    min-height: 42px;
    padding: 9px 15px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    background: #fff;
    color: var(--green);
    font-weight: 800;
    white-space: nowrap;
    cursor: pointer;
}
.family-tab.active,
.cooking-tab.active {
    background: var(--primary);
    color: #fff;
    border-color: var(--primary);
}
.family-product[hidden] {
    display: none;
}
.family-product-grid {
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(min(100%, 220px), 240px));
    justify-content: start;
}
.family-product {
    min-width: 0;
}
.theme-tab {
    min-height: 42px;
    padding: 9px 15px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    background: #fff;
    color: var(--green);
    font-weight: 800;
    white-space: nowrap;
}
.theme-tab.active {
    background: var(--green);
    color: #fff;
    border-color: var(--green);
}
.empty-state {
    grid-column: 1/-1;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 40px;
    color: var(--muted);
}
.visual-scroll-nav {
    position: sticky;
    top: calc(50vh - 260px);
    align-self: start;
    width: 200px;
    justify-self: end;
}
.type-symbol-filter {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(5, 1fr);
    gap: 6px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    padding: 8px;
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 8px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.94);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 26px rgba(66, 42, 18, 0.08);
}
.type-symbol-filter button {
    width: 100%;
    min-width: 0;
    aspect-ratio: 1;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    background: #fff;
    color: var(--green);
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: transform 0.18s ease, box-shadow 0.18s ease, background 0.18s ease, color 0.18s ease, border-color 0.18s ease;
}
.type-symbol-filter button:hover,
.type-symbol-filter button:focus-visible,
.type-symbol-filter button:active {
    background: var(--primary);
    color: #fff;
    border-color: var(--primary);
    transform: translateY(-4px) scale(1.12);
    box-shadow: 0 14px 28px rgba(143, 23, 29, 0.24);
}
.type-symbol-filter button.active {
    background: var(--primary);
    border-color: var(--primary);
    color: #fff;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 22px rgba(143, 23, 29, 0.18);
}
.type-symbol {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    line-height: 1;
    font-weight: 900;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    white-space: nowrap;
}
.type-symbol.animal {
    font-size: 1.16rem;
    transform: translateY(1px);
}
.type-symbol.animal-cow,
.type-symbol.animal-pig,
.type-symbol.animal-chicken {
    text-shadow: none;
    background: transparent;
}
.hanwoo-head {
    width: 1.48rem;
    height: 1.48rem;
    display: block;
    overflow: visible;
}
.hanwoo-face {
    fill: #b87539;
    stroke: #17110f;
    stroke-width: 4;
    stroke-linejoin: round;
}
.hanwoo-horn {
    fill: #fffaf2;
    stroke: #17110f;
    stroke-width: 4;
    stroke-linecap: round;
    stroke-linejoin: round;
}
.hanwoo-ear {
    fill: #c78347;
    stroke: #17110f;
    stroke-width: 4;
    stroke-linejoin: round;
}
.hanwoo-muzzle {
    fill: #e0ad83;
    stroke: #17110f;
    stroke-width: 3.5;
    stroke-linejoin: round;
}
.hanwoo-smile,
.hanwoo-cheek {
    fill: none;
    stroke: #17110f;
    stroke-width: 3;
    stroke-linecap: round;
}
.hanwoo-eye,
.hanwoo-nose {
    fill: #17110f;
}
.type-symbol-filter button:hover .hanwoo-face,
.type-symbol-filter button:focus-visible .hanwoo-face,
.type-symbol-filter button.active .hanwoo-face {
    fill: #c88749;
    stroke: #fffaf2;
}
.type-symbol-filter button:hover .hanwoo-ear,
.type-symbol-filter button:focus-visible .hanwoo-ear,
.type-symbol-filter button.active .hanwoo-ear {
    fill: #d09155;
    stroke: #fffaf2;
}
.type-symbol-filter button:hover .hanwoo-horn,
.type-symbol-filter button:focus-visible .hanwoo-horn,
.type-symbol-filter button.active .hanwoo-horn {
    fill: #fffaf2;
    stroke: #fff4d8;
}
.type-symbol-filter button:hover .hanwoo-muzzle,
.type-symbol-filter button:focus-visible .hanwoo-muzzle,
.type-symbol-filter button.active .hanwoo-muzzle,
.type-symbol-filter button:hover .hanwoo-smile,
.type-symbol-filter button:focus-visible .hanwoo-smile,
.type-symbol-filter button.active .hanwoo-smile,
.type-symbol-filter button:hover .hanwoo-cheek,
.type-symbol-filter button:focus-visible .hanwoo-cheek,
.type-symbol-filter button.active .hanwoo-cheek {
    stroke: #fffaf2;
}
.type-symbol-filter button:hover .hanwoo-eye,
.type-symbol-filter button:focus-visible .hanwoo-eye,
.type-symbol-filter button.active .hanwoo-eye,
.type-symbol-filter button:hover .hanwoo-nose,
.type-symbol-filter button:focus-visible .hanwoo-nose,
.type-symbol-filter button.active .hanwoo-nose {
    fill: #fffaf2;
}
.type-symbol.set {
    font-size: 0.74rem;
}
.visual-card {
    position: relative;
    border-radius: 8px;
    overflow: hidden;
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    background: #fff;
    box-shadow: 0 18px 48px rgba(66, 42, 18, 0.12);
    transition: box-shadow 0.42s ease;
    margin-top: 10px;
}
.visual-card img {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 2.8 / 4;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
}
.visual-card img.is-sliding {
    animation: photoSlideDown 0.42s ease both;
}
@keyframes photoSlideDown {
    0% {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateY(-22px);
    }
    100% {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(0);
    }
}
.visual-card span {
    display: block;
    padding: 14px;
    color: var(--green);
    font-weight: 800;
}
.product-scroll-section.is-filtering .product-card:not(.carousel-clone) {
    transition: opacity 0.24s ease, transform 0.24s ease, box-shadow 0.24s ease;
}
@media (prefers-reduced-motion: no-preference) {
    .product-card:not(.carousel-clone) {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateY(18px) scale(0.985);
        transition: opacity 0.42s ease var(--card-delay, 0ms), transform 0.42s ease var(--card-delay, 0ms), box-shadow 0.18s ease;
    }
    .product-card:not(.carousel-clone).is-card-visible {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(0) scale(1);
    }
    .product-card:not(.carousel-clone):hover {
        transform: translateY(-5px) scale(1.01);
    }
    .tag-ribbon {
        animation: tagPulse 3.8s ease-in-out infinite;
    }
    @keyframes tagPulse {
        0%, 72%, 100% { box-shadow: 0 0 0 rgba(143, 23, 29, 0); }
        82% { box-shadow: 0 0 0 7px rgba(143, 23, 29, 0.12); }
    }
}
.visual-dots {
    display: grid;
    gap: 8px;
    margin-top: 12px;
}
.visual-dots a {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    border-radius: 999px;
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    background: #fff;
    color: var(--green);
    padding: 9px 12px;
    font-weight: 800;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: transform 0.18s ease, box-shadow 0.18s ease, color 0.18s ease, border-color 0.18s ease, background 0.18s ease;
}
.visual-dots a::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: var(--primary);
    transform: translateX(-105%);
    transition: transform 0.26s ease;
    z-index: -1;
}
.visual-dots a:hover,
.visual-dots a:focus-visible,
.visual-dots a:active {
    color: #fff;
    border-color: var(--primary);
    background: var(--primary);
    transform: translateY(-4px) scale(1.04);
    box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(143, 23, 29, 0.26);
}
.visual-dots a:hover::before,
.visual-dots a:focus-visible::before,
.visual-dots a:active::before {
    transform: translateX(0);
}
.visual-dots a.active {
    background: var(--primary);
    border-color: var(--primary);
    color: #fff;
    box-shadow: 0 12px 26px rgba(143, 23, 29, 0.16);
}
.cart-toast {
    position: fixed;
    left: 50%;
    bottom: 26px;
    transform: translate(-50%, 18px);
    z-index: 2000;
    background: var(--green);
    color: #fff;
    border-radius: 999px;
    padding: 12px 18px;
    font-weight: 900;
    box-shadow: 0 18px 38px rgba(33, 79, 53, 0.24);
    opacity: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
    transition: opacity 0.22s ease, transform 0.22s ease;
}
.cart-toast.show {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translate(-50%, 0);
}
@media (max-width: 820px) {
    .products-page-snap .shop-hero,
    .products-page-snap .product-scroll-section {
        scroll-margin-top: 72px;
    }
    .products-page-snap .product-scroll-section {
        min-height: calc(100vh - 62px);
    }
    .shop-hero { padding: 44px 16px 28px; }
    .shop-section { padding: 28px 16px 20px; }
    .family-tabs,
    .cooking-tabs {
        flex-wrap: nowrap;
        overflow-x: auto;
        padding-bottom: 2px;
    }
    .family-product-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    .product-grid.is-carousel > .product-card,
    .product-grid.is-carousel > .family-product {
        flex-basis: min(82vw, 320px);
    }
    .bg-alt {
        margin-top: 0;
        padding: 28px 16px 20px;
    }
}
@media (max-width: 1099px) {
    .shop-scroll-layout {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        padding: 0;
    }
    .market-belief,
    .visual-scroll-nav {
        position: static;
        margin: 20px 16px 0;
        min-height: auto;
    }
    .market-belief {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 110px 1fr;
        gap: 14px;
        align-items: center;
    }
    .market-belief img {
        width: 110px;
        height: 86px;
        margin: 0;
    }
    .market-belief p,
    .belief-list {
        grid-column: 1 / -1;
    }
    .visual-scroll-nav {
        display: block;
        order: -1;
    }
    .visual-card,
    .visual-dots {
        display: none;
    }
    .type-symbol-filter {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        margin: 0 0 12px;
        padding: 8px;
    }
    .type-symbol-filter button {
        width: 42px;
        height: 42px;
        flex: 0 0 42px;
    }
}
</style>

<script>
document.documentElement.classList.add('products-page-snap');
window.addEventListener('beforeunload', () => {
    document.documentElement.classList.remove('products-page-snap');
});
</script>
